Ninu sevimpagaa nerpina prabhuvaa{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Naa jeevithamuna nee maatalanu vinutaye chaalani
Yerigitini naa kanneetitho nee paadamulanu
Kaduguta nerpina oh naa prabhuvaa{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Vyardha parachitini naa sarvamunu swaardamutho
